1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,043
Pause at the end of the day.

2
00:00:02,043 --> 00:00:04,690
Let your body know that this day is
ending.

3
00:00:04,690 --> 00:00:06,966
Take a slow breath in.

4
00:00:09,966 --> 00:00:11,870
And let it out.

5
00:00:11,870 --> 00:00:15,028
Notice one thing you are still carrying.

6
00:00:15,028 --> 00:00:15,864
A thought.

7
00:00:15,864 --> 00:00:16,839
A feeling.

8
00:00:16,839 --> 00:00:18,372
A worry.

9
00:00:18,372 --> 00:00:20,648
A conversation.

10
00:00:20,648 --> 00:00:23,434
A part that is still working.

11
00:00:23,434 --> 00:00:29,807
Now say gently: Thank you for trying to
help me today. You do not have to keep

12
00:00:29,807 --> 00:00:31,793
working so hard tonight.

13
00:00:31,793 --> 00:00:36,576
Imagine setting down one small piece of
what you are carrying.

14
00:00:42,576 --> 00:00:42,576
<break time="3s" />

15
00:00:42,576 --> 00:00:43,923
Not everything.

16
00:00:43,923 --> 00:00:45,502
Just one piece.

17
00:00:45,502 --> 00:00:50,192
Now ask: What helped me today, even a
little?

18
00:00:56,192 --> 00:00:56,192
<break time="3s" />

19
00:00:56,192 --> 00:00:58,886
Let yourself notice one thing.

20
00:00:58,886 --> 00:01:01,812
Take one final breath.

21
00:01:01,812 --> 00:01:06,735
And allow yourself to close this day with
a little more kindness.

22
00:01:15,735 --> 00:01:15,735
<break time="3s" />

